column5: Leaving Friday! Today me and the boys are doing some last minute shopping and refreshing the line on the reels. Tomorrow will be the longest day at work :/ What do you think the Walleyes will be doing Saturday?
Committing suicide!! Safe travels and good fishing!

Thinking........." These knuckleheads are going to feed us again. Can you believe it Earl? Earl , did you hear what I said........these knuckleheads are going to feed us....... Uhmmm, Earl , where did you go ? "
Beautiful Evergreen Lodge on Lac Seul

the walleyes are probably still resting from all that sexual activity from spawning 10 days from now well rested and very hungry they will be active on a serious note does anyone know when the spawn occurred around grassy narrows on English river 1 hr north of kenora ?? leaving for last resort on 5/28 out of Chicago will report all guys have good safe trips jim wolf Chicago boys
